Class DefaultImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdesktop.swingworker.SwingWorker<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, java.util.concurrent.Future<java.lang.String>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocEtatProviderImporter, ImporterWithXSLBeforeSplitFile

    public class DefaultImporter
extends EtatImporteur
    This class imports a document in the underlying data layer. First it splits the document in small files that contains only one importable element. Then, if the "Etat" configuration defines an Xsl to apply before importing, it applies it. Finally, it delegates import to the data layer. This class has been fully-rewritten since Xemelios 3.0, replacing the old DefaultImporteur one.
    Since:
    3.0
